title: Engineering Manager Pop Quiz #1: What Would You Do?
description: What do you do as an engineering manager when there's tension brewing between junior and senior engineers?

title: Engineering Manager Pop Quiz #3: What Would You Do?

description: Your star employee just gave their notice. Ugh. How do you handle their resignation?
